              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Neptunium-oxide, Pu-239 impurity content is less 1.E-4",
                " -1.E-5 % of weight.",
                " Two samples of 9.0 mg weight each were heated at 1000-",
                "110 deg C, then packed in Al capsules.",
                "1-st samples was irradiated by thermal neutrons of",
                " 6.E+13 n/sec/cm*2 neutron beam during 250 hr.",
                "2-nd sample was covered by Cd of 1mm and irradiated",
                "during 500 hr by neutrons of average effective energy",
                "> 0.5 MeV and 6.E+12 n/sec/cm**2."
